    <node id="NIST.CSWP.29.pdf">
      <data key="d0">NIST.CSWP.29.pdf</data>
      <data key="d1">document</data>
      <data key="d2">NIST.CSWP.29.pdf is a document related to the NIST Cybersecurity Framework version 2.0, specifically as the source file for "The NIST Cybersecurity Framework (CSF) 2.0". It contains 32 pages and is associated with cybersecurity guidelines, certification resources, and training materials for professionals. The document was parsed using PyMuPDF, indicating it's a PDF format file. It also contains information about the NIST CSWP 29 guidelines and the NIST Cybersecurity Framework (CSF) version 20, which includes continuous nature of cybersecurity for organizational stages.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-a1685ea14462551d4e0ca8c4ebd817b7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-78d7272f17d4adab91f99606404c911f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-52978ce057f3b7a004200fd6c66d7288&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-de226951c463af74dc9833ddd3cec4ee&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4aac65a4923c5272ea41ff8304d7c75d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6fd198cb863de8f31f9ae6a2d92b1914&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-027f4189bd6b5dfed068ce73fa4bf7fa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1006bc0fb3f33493a9bb69116ebeeb94&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-14fce07db5d5d98da204e5564aa52a02&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5ff07271093466ab167760cb8ac11eda&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e6937a0dea6bdccfd0acd899789297fc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4564cb8a99fed5101a1ffbf03b124246&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6a3947c70b3ebbaf91b10a9066eeaf10&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-602aa4ccbd230d5cc27c154e57ecd301&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-827f48355d04a2a9eaac5548458d8e8c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ea8834e456266a90dc1fcf85576cb3fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8b193a13851e6929cbb22da5ab360704&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-324e7818307e26fab966afee243e2645&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4893f0b02c584c1055b59d8cddfca8df&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ef0c2be3ac1a640a1e4f1a6297267b75&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf46d9eb463a9d027228452649d3d4e3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4b4f557b83cdbcb0aae797dc04ef0cde&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7394049c069819ca015b82ca0e5bf283&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b73552e0583c94de6a1ae7ce97f9941c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e142782c0b1f1e12e441bc558839e38e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-677447a4356867486f88700f12794eb7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ba7b2d86ee394df6f581db52e93726f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3a1c2f94461354c30294c3c0828925fa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d2a8cc9c75c9b5a3099bb67ae5079e55&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5cf0ecace48f517f2845c25e229bcaa2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-845403f5258ee6652ecfcfb89ed85f40&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-29018601b2284d1aa80189393eacf3d8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cc2c17308d80e7fb4a18acd6cc98aa96&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e5e301f0e25e3c41d4681d4c01fb9202&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-87e6df0c0d226b569e5364963e932ff2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ba4195b5319182c599352607302e77cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d595e972f89f1931b8d54930d4b17946&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-727c8eddde5cc81ee945e9ee3490be7d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c6f7bae29996027737c7dc965ea0239&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a248dcfc17282d26bafbf027f779165f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9c5c7e07a24d3