    <node id="The NIST Cybersecurity Framework (CSF) 2.0">
      <data key="d0">The NIST Cybersecurity Framework (CSF) 2.0</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">The NIST Cybersecurity Framework (CSF) 2.0, also known as CSF version 2.0, is a comprehensive cybersecurity guideline document published by the National Institute of Standards and Technology (NIST). It provides detailed guidance on managing cyber risks for organizations across various technology environments and types of IT systems. The framework consists of several key components including Core elements which outline the five main functions: Identify, Protect, Detect, Respond, and Recover; Profiles and Tiers that define how an organization can apply the Framework to different settings based on risk tolerance and resources available; Online Resources aimed at supporting practitioners in applying the CSF effectively; and Risk Communication strategies for sharing information among stakeholders. It aims to enhance governance, security operations, and risk management within organizations, offering a flexible approach adaptable to unique risks, technologies, and mission considerations across sectors and countries. The NIST Cybersecurity Framework 2.0 is an updated version of previous cybersecurity guidelines and standards, focusing on improving the cybersecurity posture of organizations by aligning their governance, risk management, and incident response activities.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-a1685ea14462551d4e0ca8c4ebd817b7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-52978ce057f3b7a004200fd6c66d7288&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-de226951c463af74dc9833ddd3cec4ee&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4aac65a4923c5272ea41ff8304d7c75d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-027f4189bd6b5dfed068ce73fa4bf7fa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-14fce07db5d5d98da204e5564aa52a02&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5ff07271093466ab167760cb8ac11eda&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e6937a0dea6bdccfd0acd899789297fc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4564cb8a99fed5101a1ffbf03b124246&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6a3947c70b3ebbaf91b10a9066eeaf10&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cb4b577ab4ab56fceba946faf29a43fd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ea8834e456266a90dc1fcf85576cb3fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4893f0b02c584c1055b59d8cddfca8df&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf46d9eb463a9d027228452649d3d4e3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4b4f557b83cdbcb0aae797dc04ef0cde&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7394049c069819ca015b82ca0e5bf283&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b73552e0583c94de6a1ae7ce97f9941c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e142782c0b1f1e12e441bc558839e38e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3a1c2f94461354c30294c3c0828925fa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-845403f5258ee6652ecfcfb89ed85f40&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-29018601b2284d1aa80189393eacf3d8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cc2c17308d80e7fb4a18acd6cc98aa96&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-87e6df0c0d226b569e5364963e932ff2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ba4195b5319182c599352607302e77cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d595e972f89f1931b8d54930d4b17946&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-727c8eddde5cc81ee945e9ee3490be7d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a248dcfc17282d26bafbf027f779165f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-059bca7035caffc2433e27299fca0d41&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0ada8334c40c41430fa9296968b88ece&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fa363d8ef99097ed7573a56ea4881f85&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dba679cd2a87fd4be3fe1a3614ca9bc6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ea01d86e7c90396acabcbc9758c9a457&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6bc48c91d9bf95547aba1636fc17956f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-53d74513f9b4bf4e857dc587f365cfcf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d1058d7d75178b661f062c47165b429&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41db6094ad592f0dccdd54c40a045eeb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0a7038b7fceeb3ee037a01a5090cad1e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1bd8099546d6ba4f3178525229495d88&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6c7a572812b3b9c78377fb00817f0109&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0af2b2ff693fc69321fb689063551953&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c4669401a25e4