    <node id="NIST Cybersecurity Framework (CSF)">
      <data key="d0">NIST Cybersecurity Framework (CSF)</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">NIST Cybersecurity Framework (NIST-CSF) is a structured approach to managing cybersecurity risks and ensuring compliance with organizational goals and regulatory requirements. It serves as a resource for various sectors including industry, government, academia, and nonprofit organizations. NIST-CSF 2.0 provides guidelines for improving cybersecurity posture, enhancing governance, and aligning security practices with business needs. The framework is updated annually by the National Institute of Standards and Technology (NIST), offering comprehensive guidance on managing cybersecurity activities and risks. It represents a hierarchical structure encompassing six core functions in cybersecurity: Identify, Protect, Detect, Respond, Recover, and Authenticate. Additionally, NIST-CSF offers practices to improve an organization's security posture through various elements such as Security Objectives, Security Maturity Model, Security Assessments, and Communication Activities.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-3ae9e3476dacda5dbc0b092eee310a64&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e234621b7f425933aeb1e42b348c4a32&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3aabc114a079783ccc75385f8a3d0e34&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4be9a68c3dc47aaf5018803479dc6e00&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f13c4bf957696002d1910106b96f51e7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-44d7ecc33923fb7c0e17377dacc68586&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d5111c9032a1e5655f2f7c4cc2070ee&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5cf0ecace48f517f2845c25e229bcaa2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6e0d0175165f5302cc1e6ae4c641c34d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6632abeaa757531b99f060efde3a5149&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0fc3ee5b64dc4bd0233d867af22d889a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2466c4a13bd6306d3a09498f94e8d834&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5b0ca6812cf2474799c4e95a396ae1df&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3170620e5eb165738cb05be72d4b8b50&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3d6779a3859e0dd92a32b8ad4c053249&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9729c8c1d6541456d51571ac5dbf3d41&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-53d2c96376b3ade38af88a24dd1c8d3e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-326fc9fc709f7b8db1a373ea928e6d23&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a0af414c8f4b7cd2e2ada0f0299d7b13&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5fe8375d52689cccf79f112601918c4b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e9e3ee337079a2ad4117c08435d5a020&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-701fbd369bbdbe7ae4a94457a4cfdb1e</data>
