    <node id="NIST">
      <data key="d0">NIST</data>
      <data key="d1">organization</data>
      <data key="d2">NIST (National Institute of Standards and Technology) is a federal agency within the U.S. government responsible for developing and maintaining cybersecurity frameworks and standards. It is known for creating the NIST Cybersecurity Framework (CSF), which it maintains as well. Additionally, NIST is involved in issuing documents related to cybersecurity standards and practices, often focusing on security protocols and guidelines. As a standards organization, NIST plays a crucial role in establishing best practices and frameworks for securing systems against cyber threats.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-ef5db71b90df0c19b8c356aeee744fc6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bdcf1715979a7e31cc08a2fbd03306f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ef0c2be3ac1a640a1e4f1a6297267b75&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7b99d228b63c2a53a2dbaef1c5e77109&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4dd323a57a5e201dbbabc38ad150d0a1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7e02b7aa698b9c023dac6aead366390a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-02223016f864c217915db457dc244cc1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-56f1498ba6ce64eefdb5e139e2a93c31&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0a7038b7fceeb3ee037a01a5090cad1e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-03314f72fe084c6cbbb45e9c54ba4d79&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1bd8099546d6ba4f3178525229495d88&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0af2b2ff693fc69321fb689063551953&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cb91369f464ed519ed771389796ff36c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b85f1f3296b3a84e2b5e99897e486e55&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fa283b24cceb950da35d448426784da4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6c34e6e4f53111e1e0df93b233b83242&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-07520e3378ec637954e3df08cc822bf2</data>
