    <node id="Carbon-Fiber Spikes">
      <data key="d0">Carbon-Fiber Spikes</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Noah Carter used carbon-fiber spikes to enhance his performance during the race at the World Athletics Championship.&lt;SEP&gt;The carbon-fiber spikes are the advanced sprinting shoes used by Noah Carter during his 100m race at the World Athletics Championship.&lt;SEP&gt;The carbon-fiber spikes used by Noah Carter in his sprint are considered advanced athletic equipment.&lt;SEP&gt;Noah Carter used carbon-fiber spikes to enhance performance during the race.&lt;SEP&gt;Noah Carter used carbon-fiber spikes to enhance his performance during the 100m sprint at the World Athletics Championship.&lt;SEP&gt;Carbon-fiber spikes are advanced sprinting shoes that provide enhanced speed and traction, used by Noah Carter during the competition.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-027f4189bd6b5dfed068ce73fa4bf7fa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ba7b2d86ee394df6f581db52e93726f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a248dcfc17282d26bafbf027f779165f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0ada8334c40c41430fa9296968b88ece&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-431d81acdf3085b24870b661be16b4f1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf2f43ae6609115d347760a621948298&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f13c4bf957696002d1910106b96f51e7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ef0c2be3ac1a640a1e4f1a6297267b75&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c6f7bae29996027737c7dc965ea0239&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-525996cd68eb04d57d90b7c23e0a2eb9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e1e59bd045467f10e8decfe40ce94095</data>
