    <node id="Implementation Examples">
      <data key="d0">Implementation Examples</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Implementation Examples offer illustrations of how an organization can achieve certain outcomes using the NIST Cybersecurity Framework (CSF).&lt;SEP&gt;This refers to the specific examples provided for achieving outcomes within the framework of the NIST Cybersecurity Work Proficiency (CSWP) 20.</data>
