    <node id="NIST Cybersecurity Framework (CSF) 2.0">
      <data key="d0">NIST Cybersecurity Framework (CSF) 2.0</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">NIST Cybersecurity Framework (CSF) 2.0, or simply CSF 2.0, is a comprehensive cybersecurity framework published by the National Institute of Standards and Technology (NIST). It aims to assist various industries, sectors, and entities in managing and mitigating their cybersecurity risks. The document outlines a structured approach to addressing cybersecurity through policies, processes, and procedures, and it defines functions, categories, and subcategories related to cybersecurity management. As an updated version of NIST's previous framework, CSF 2.0 provides comprehensive guidance for effective cybersecurity governance. It serves as a reference for managing cybersecurity risks within organizations.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-ef5db71b90df0c19b8c356aeee744fc6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6b64acf47e907c74febec8f45419fe1b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fb41292c4ded4903f8bc597010d71497&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-580e95c1b11fd2d0ea198e331b32c67a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9462b7987d4d746e2aac0436a0a4dbdc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3dc7cce2d8eeb05148bc616ed780f9d7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5659a2d45be7952195aa14cef14fb7d0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9d7b00744edbdc7a7228592a2da49aab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6df9f1b0cef4c18b6c32ef41a1ed7ea9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-431d81acdf3085b24870b661be16b4f1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-86583643b07c1568b52f107766c93525&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e5b4b647cfc83bd14c03d0b7165619c5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-03314f72fe084c6cbbb45e9c54ba4d79&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-09e5ce010011a1c01ac378dc9f7c42dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0af2b2ff693fc69321fb689063551953&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-12270c419c1c9d3b9a5113eea36aa55c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-951a269034b4853c739e0abb73cea1ec&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b5140bbf92d407fa00cfc9038b05bff6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-17b50b473f7a6de56879895cc1b30e97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f7ec5a71104b40f4aee23b0b819defd7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a51ce8efe7fb626ad33e30bcecf33e03&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-355d53d98836023fb3aa20ca11c32b0e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3bc458dd28316bb4e7070e39b19c5b38&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a1fc7a8b60bff365d2d131c98e7308c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9f4c79c195ee275405e879e10588c0c8</data>
