    <node id="Title: The NIST Cybersecurity Framework (CSF) 2.0">
      <data key="d0">Title: The NIST Cybersecurity Framework (CSF) 2.0</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">The NIST Cybersecurity Framework (CSF) 2.0 is a versioned cybersecurity framework published by the National Institute of Standards and Technology (NIST). This version includes updates to enhance its relevance for modern cyber threats and strategies. It was released in 2020, aligning with ongoing efforts to improve organizational resilience against cyber risks. The document discusses various components such as Identify, Protect, Detect, Respond, Recover, and Govern, detailing how organizations can implement these elements to protect their digital assets effectively.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-cb4b577ab4ab56fceba946faf29a43fd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-324e7818307e26fab966afee243e2645&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b73552e0583c94de6a1ae7ce97f9941c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e5e301f0e25e3c41d4681d4c01fb9202&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fa363d8ef99097ed7573a56ea4881f85&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6c7a572812b3b9c78377fb00817f0109&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1dc8b3afb371c358a4a849868e65e091&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-25eb93c68ce1a37ae6e09b271db64dc9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b320a0226c391d26a3f52ad2ed36770f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e1e59bd045467f10e8decfe40ce94095&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf46d9eb463a9d027228452649d3d4e3</data>
      <data key="d4">parsed_data/NIST.CSWP.29.md</data>
      <data key="d5">1773879927</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
