    <node id="NIST Cybersecurity Framework">
      <data key="d0">NIST Cybersecurity Framework</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">The NIST Cybersecurity Framework is a widely adopted security standard that provides a structured approach to managing and reducing cybersecurity risk.&lt;SEP&gt;The NIST Cybersecurity Framework (CSF) is a structured approach to manage cybersecurity risks within an organizational environment.&lt;SEP&gt;The NIST Cybersecurity Framework (CSF) 2.0 is a set of guidelines for managing cybersecurity.&lt;SEP&gt;The NIST Cybersecurity Framework (CSF) is a set of guidelines for managing cybersecurity risk.</data>
