    <node id="Repeatable (Tier 3)">
      <data key="d0">Repeatable (Tier 3)</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">An organization may use the Repeatable Tier for practices that are risk-informed and repeatable, which aligns with ongoing management of cybersecurity risks.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-1a1497d01e433b4c62c0be4ed37b11e3</data>
      <data key="d4">parsed_data/NIST.CSWP.29.md</data>
      <data key="d5">1773879942</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
