      <data key="d0">Adaptive (Tier 4)</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">The Adaptive Tier denotes an organization’s approach to managing cybersecurity risks is agile and reflects an adaptive strategy, moving beyond traditional risk management methods.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-1a1497d01e433b4c62c0be4ed37b11e3</data>
      <data key="d4">parsed_data/NIST.CSWP.29.md</data>
