      <data key="d0">ID.AM-01</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">ID.AM-01 refers to maintaining inventories of hardware managed by an organization, ensuring systematic tracking and management.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-e1e59bd045467f10e8decfe40ce94095</data>
      <data key="d4">parsed_data/NIST.CSWP.29.md</data>
