      <data key="d2">The NIST Cybersecurity Framework (CSF) 2.0 is described in this text-based document, specifically a PDF file. The kind field indicates it contains textual information related to the NIST Cybersecurity Framework version 2.0. It serves as both an educational and regulatory resource within cybersecurity, including quick start guides and other supplementary resources that form part of its core content. This publication is categorized under "text", emphasizing it primarily consists of written material rather than multimedia forms.</data>
